{"tid":2190784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"環時：若戰爭攤牌，中國一定讓印度比1962年失敗更慘痛","createTime":"2020-09-06T03:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T11:10:10.000Z","uid":137088,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7c5eed1dec0781e57a23d7dd8f775aff84d363","tid":2190784,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/09/06/nmy4xp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F09%2F06%2Fnmy4xp.png&h=23c1d01c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/議事廳/517910/中印衝突-環時-若戰爭攤牌-中國一定讓印度比1962年失敗更慘痛?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3%2F517910%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E8%8B%A5%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E6%94%A4%E7%89%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%AE%93%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%AF%941962%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E6%9B%B4%E6%85%98%E7%97%9B%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=0948c6b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/議事廳/517910/中印衝突-環時-若戰爭攤牌-中國一定讓印度比1962年失敗更慘痛?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n中印邊境局勢再度緊張，印度8月31日指責解放軍試圖越界，又稱挫敗了解放軍的活動。對此，中國外交部發言人趙立堅在則否認中方越界，而解放軍西部戰區則在8月31日晚間表示，印軍8月31日在班公湖南岸、熱欽山口附近再次非法越線佔控，公然挑釁，嚴重侵犯中國領土主權，嚴重破壞中印邊境地區和平穩定。<br />\n《環球時報》發表社評稱，中國對印方的機會主義表現必須強硬回擊。該社評指，如果印度想用戰爭方式做攤牌，解放軍一定能夠讓印軍遭受比1962年更慘痛的失敗。"},{"pid":"7ebfe2d6c765377db7f1ddab6fc59aff2d34a3e7","tid":2190784,"uid":156751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"菁英嘴"},{"pid":"fb6b6afdbfb43870c3ed0d1f06696d5850e8c0df","tid":2190784,"uid":224533,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SvUtOj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"